			Profile
			
			Biography:
Dr&nbsp;Xiangrui&nbsp;Liu&nbsp;gained&nbsp;his&nbsp;PhD&nbsp;from&nbsp;the&nbsp;University&nbsp;of&nbsp;Nottingham,&nbsp;School&nbsp;of&nbsp;Pharmacy(Top&nbsp;Pharmacy&nbsp;school&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;UK)&nbsp;in&nbsp;2011&nbsp;
under&nbsp;the&nbsp;supervision&nbsp;of&nbsp;Professor&nbsp;Shudong&nbsp;Wang.&nbsp;This&nbsp;was&nbsp;followed&nbsp;by&nbsp;a&nbsp;period&nbsp;of&nbsp;postdoctoral&nbsp;training&nbsp;in&nbsp;Cambridge(2011-2013)&nbsp;under&nbsp;the&nbsp;guidance&nbsp;of&nbsp;Sir&nbsp;Professor&nbsp;Alan&nbsp;Fersht(FRS).&nbsp;He&nbsp;joined&nbsp;Zhejiang&nbsp;University&nbsp;in&nbsp;2013&nbsp;and&nbsp;was&nbsp;promoted&nbsp;to&nbsp;Associate&nbsp;
Professor&nbsp;shortly.&nbsp;&nbsp;
He&nbsp;is&nbsp;currently&nbsp;an&nbsp;academic&nbsp;staff&nbsp;member&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Institute&nbsp;of&nbsp;Bioengineering,&nbsp;Department&nbsp;of&nbsp;Chemical&nbsp;and&nbsp;Biological&nbsp;Engineering.
&nbsp;
EditorialBoardmemberof&nbsp;DARUJournalofPharmaceuticalSciences&nbsp;
&nbsp;
			
				
			Researchwork
			
			Hisresearchinterestsfocusonnoveldrugdeliverysystems,molecularpharmaceutics,modernformulationsoftraditionalChinesemedicineanddiscoveryofantitumoragents.


